See Helen Branswell's tweets (https://twitter.com/HelenBranswell) on these recent violent events at the Ebola treatment centers against the progress that has been made elsewhere in North Kivu-Ituri. See her graphics on case numbers in the North Kivu outbreak. - Mod.LK]

